mention this requirement initially.

570
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:30,919
That's because Captain Su

571
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:31,959
simply didn't know

572
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:33,119
all girls in this world

573
00:30:33,120 --> 00:30:35,760
