626
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:41,080
Focus.

627
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:54,520
♪In a fleeting moment♪

628
00:35:55,760 --> 00:36:02,680
♪Like the rhythmic beats of connection♪

629
00:36:04,160 --> 00:36:06,320
♪Unconsciously♪

630
